short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension that replaces 'Prompt Engineer' with 'person that can type questions to ChatGPT'

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sick of seeing people calling themselves "Prompt Engineers"? This extension will replace any website text of "Prompt Engineer" to "person that can type questions to ChatGPT".

For added irony, this Chrome extension was written entirely by ChatGPT, because I have no idea how to make a Chrome extension - however - I am a person that can type questions to ChatGPT.
